773
00:36:54,830 --> 00:36:56,264
Of course.

774
00:36:56,331 --> 00:37:00,100
I mean, it's--it's a matter
of opinion. I...

775
00:37:01,935 --> 00:37:03,138
You feeling all right?

776
00:37:03,139 --> 00:37:05,639
I'm fine, yes.
That's--I'm fine.

777
00:37:05,706 --> 00:37:07,440
