781
00:37:12,248 --> 00:37:14,851
You led us right to it.
I did not.

782
00:37:14,919 --> 00:37:17,020
Yes, you did.
You led us right to it,

783
00:37:17,088 --> 00:37:18,090
And how could you do that
if you didn't kill her?

784
00:37:18,191 --> 00:37:20,591
That's the most--

785
00:37:21,258 --> 00:37:23,493
That's the most ridiculous...

786
