So it's over.

789
00:37:48,650 --> 00:37:50,117
Yeah, it's over.

790
00:37:50,184 --> 00:37:52,719
That's too bad.
It was fun.

791
00:37:52,786 --> 00:37:55,454
Yeah. How you gonna top
