807
00:38:44,730 --> 00:38:48,298
Self-righteous bitch.

808
00:38:48,366 --> 00:38:51,967
<i>Westhoff finds out I was</i>
<i>taking out his top earner,</i>

809
00:38:52,035 --> 00:38:54,836
