813
00:39:06,380 --> 00:39:08,815
It was me or her.

814
00:39:08,883 --> 00:39:10,817
You have to understand that.

815
00:39:10,885 --> 00:39:13,853
Someone gives you that choice,
you choose you every time.

816
00:39:13,921 --> 00:39:17,123
